caption.body: The increasing demands of a father’s daily routine demonstrate how easy it is to lose sight of what, and who, our original tasks and responsibilities were intended to serve in this metaphor for modern parenthood and its hazards.  See "Tend" by Tom Judd and Ed Barrett, now playing in the Video Arts gallery, located pre-security in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/2PczW2v . . . #VideoArtsSFOM #video #tend #animation #illustration #parenting #father #daughter #TomJudd #Ed Barrett
